Situational awareness.

788
00:37:50,561 --> 00:37:52,562
Elijah's not gonna be
happy about this.

789
00:37:52,563 --> 00:37:54,523
Elijah brought his own bat.

790
00:37:54,524 --> 00:37:55,899
Wait, wait, wait!
Why are you doing this?!

791
00:37:55,900 --> 00:37:57,193
Stop! Stop!

792
00:38:00,071 --> 00:38:01,905
The strangest thing
happened yesterday

793
00:38:01,906 --> 00:38:04,033
after you left
that witness' home.

794
00:38:05,910 --> 00:38:07,744
Cops swooped in
and arrested him.

795
00:38:07,745 --> 00:38:09,704
It was almost like someone
wanted to keep him

796
00:38:09,705 --> 00:38:11,832
out of harm's way.

797
00:38:11,833 --> 00:38:13,626
It's like you were
working against me.

798
00:38:14,919 --> 00:38:16,462
Are you really this stupid?

799
00:38:22,510 --> 00:38:24,135
You told me
to make the witness go away.

800
00:38:24,136 --> 00:38:26,764
That's what I did!
I took him off the board!

801
00:38:27,890 --> 00:38:30,225
I got him arrested for
an illegal weapons violation.

802
00:38:30,226 --> 00:38:32,102
There is no way
he can testify now.

803
00:38:32,103 --> 00:38:33,812
His credibility's shot.

804
00:38:33,813 --> 00:38:34,896
And as an added bonus,

805
00:38:34,897 --> 00:38:37,108
you didn't have
to commit another crime.

806
00:38:40,945 --> 00:38:42,863
Oh.

807
00:38:42,864 --> 00:38:44,615
Well, that changes things.

808
00:38:50,705 --> 00:38:53,290
You need to work on
your communication skills,

809
00:38:53,291 --> 00:38:56,586
'cause this beating's based
on your lack of transparency.

810
00:39:01,883 --> 00:39:03,925
Are we good?

811
00:39:03,926 --> 00:39:05,719
Yeah.

812
00:39:05,720 --> 00:39:06,762
For now.

813
00:39:08,556 --> 00:39:09,724
Great work.

814
00:39:20,401 --> 00:39:22,569
Hey.

815
00:39:22,570 --> 00:39:23,571
Hey.

816
00:39:24,739 --> 00:39:27,616
Welcome back to the land
of the living.

817
00:39:27,617 --> 00:39:29,159
Doc said you were
pretty banged up,

818
00:39:29,160 --> 00:39:31,661
but lucky you ‐‐
no broken bones.

819
00:39:31,662 --> 00:39:33,121
Really?

820
00:39:33,122 --> 00:39:34,706
It feels like
everything's broken.

821
00:39:34,707 --> 00:39:36,459
They have meds for that.

822
00:39:38,336 --> 00:39:39,836
Great job out there.

823
00:39:39,837 --> 00:39:41,004
We got him.

824
00:39:41,005 --> 00:39:42,130
No, you got him.

825
00:39:42,131 --> 00:39:44,717
Yeah, after he got me.

826
00:39:47,762 --> 00:39:49,429
There she is.

827
00:39:49,430 --> 00:39:50,890
Hi.

828
00:39:54,602 --> 00:39:56,270
Come here.

829
00:39:57,229 --> 00:39:58,897
Ow. Oh, sorry.

830
00:39:58,898 --> 00:40:00,106
No, no. It's okay, it's okay.

831
00:40:00,107 --> 00:40:01,816
It's a good hurt. I can take it.

832
00:40:01,817 --> 00:40:03,068
I can take it.

833
00:40:03,069 --> 00:40:04,277
I can't take it.

834
00:40:04,278 --> 00:40:06,446
Mm.

835
00:40:06,447 --> 00:40:08,782
I'm so relieved you're okay.

836
00:40:08,783 --> 00:40:09,908
Oh, it's nothing.

837
00:40:09,909 --> 00:40:11,368
Just a couple more war wounds

838
00:40:11,369 --> 00:40:13,286
I can flaunt in bed.

839
00:40:13,287 --> 00:40:14,955
Speaking of,
what are you doing here?

840
00:40:14,956 --> 00:40:16,247
Aren't you supposed
to be in bed?

841
00:40:16,248 --> 00:40:18,416
Mm, yeah.

842
00:40:18,417 --> 00:40:19,668
Scoot over.

843
00:40:19,669 --> 00:40:21,252
Done.

844
00:40:21,253 --> 00:40:23,047
Okay.

845
00:40:24,799 --> 00:40:25,925
Okay.

846
00:40:33,224 --> 00:40:35,100
You got him.

847
00:40:35,101 --> 00:40:36,559
I told you I would.

848
00:40:36,560 --> 00:40:38,103
Oh, no.

849
00:40:38,104 --> 00:40:40,105
"I told you so" is so much worse

850
00:40:40,106 --> 00:40:41,189
than "I promise."

851
00:40:41,190 --> 00:40:43,566
Really? A relationship killer.

852
00:40:43,567 --> 00:40:45,235
100%.

853
00:40:45,236 --> 00:40:47,613
I'm gonna need some kind
of cheat sheet, I think.

854
00:40:52,076 --> 00:40:53,118
Seriously, I can't believe

855
00:40:53,119 --> 00:40:54,619
you bought out
the entire gift shop.

856
00:40:54,620 --> 00:40:56,496
What? You've been
in the hospital before.

857
00:40:56,497 --> 00:40:58,331
You know how boring it can be.

858
00:40:58,332 --> 00:41:00,375
What did you get him? Nothing.

859
00:41:00,376 --> 00:41:02,460
I'll just put my name on yours.

860
00:41:02,461 --> 00:41:03,962
Unbelievable.

861
00:41:03,963 --> 00:41:05,130
Hey, we're going
back out on patrol

862
00:41:05,131 --> 00:41:07,007
after we're done visiting
with Nolan, right?

863
00:41:07,008 --> 00:41:08,133
Lucy.

864
00:41:08,134 --> 00:41:09,968
Mm‐hmm. What?

865
00:41:09,969 --> 00:41:11,386
You know, I have a bet to win.

866
00:41:11,387 --> 00:41:12,637
Okay, can we just call it off?

867
00:41:12,638 --> 00:41:14,514
Police work is too important
to turn into a game.

868
00:41:14,515 --> 00:41:16,307
You're just worried
you're gonna lose.

869
00:41:16,308 --> 00:41:18,393
Sure. If that's what you need to
hear, let's go with that.

870
00:41:18,394 --> 00:41:19,644
Wait, hold on.

871
00:41:19,645 --> 00:41:22,689
Since when did you become
the noble one here?

872
00:41:22,690 --> 00:41:25,025
Does this mean
we're square on our bet?

873
00:41:25,026 --> 00:41:26,109
Fine.

874
00:41:26,110 --> 00:41:27,318
Nobody wins.

875
00:41:27,319 --> 00:41:29,488
But the basket is only from me.

876
00:41:36,162 --> 00:41:37,203
Where you been?

877
00:41:37,204 --> 00:41:39,123
I thought you were gonna
be here for bedtime.

878
00:41:41,625 --> 00:41:43,669
Sorry, I‐I got stuck on a call.

879
00:41:53,554 --> 00:41:55,264
Angela.

880
00:42:04,231 --> 00:42:06,691
What's wrong?

881
00:42:06,692 --> 00:42:08,360
I screwed up.

882
00:42:09,904 --> 00:42:11,322
I need help.

